gentRuntimeList 包含所有资源\\n1426: - **AND** Items 数组包含所有 AgentRuntime 对象\\n1427: \\n1428: #### Scenario: AR-041-002-H — Watch AgentRuntime 资源变化\\n1429: \\n1430: - **GIVEN** 有效的 ListOptions 配置\\n1431: - **WHEN** 调用 `Watch(ctx, metav1.ListOptions{})`\\n1432: - **THEN** 返回 watch.Interface\\n1433: - **AND** 可以接收资源变更事件\\n1434: \\n1435: #### Scenario: AR-041-002-I — Patch AgentRuntime 资源\\n1436: \\n1437: - ...\n  Line 19: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775884935902,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28502d3eeffej2CLU52co2DfCk\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7afda121001RmjkbMfBuGURCt\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7afd8d3e001uLw5Z5ysv4n9pW\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28502d3eeffej2CLU52co2DfCk\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I'll create the tasks.md checklist for AR-041 E2E integration tests:\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775884935901,\"end\":1775884935901}}}\n  Line 20: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775884967404,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28502d3eeffej2CLU52co2DfCk\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7afda2df001HqizEiTApf0n15\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7afd8d3e001uLw5Z5ysv4n9pW\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28502d3eeffej2CLU52co2DfCk\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_c778ba84e15f4e699b146080\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Tasks: AR-041 — E2E 集成测试\\n\\n**Module**: `test/e2e`  \\n**Language**: Go  \\n**Size**: L  \\n**Status**: [Stage ST-3 completed]\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Phase 1: Clientset 创建与配置测试\\n\\n- [ ] T001: 创建 test/e2e 目录结构\\n- [ ] T002: 实现 clientset_test.go - 测试 NewForConfig 创建标准 Clientset\\n- [ ] T003: 实现 clientset_test.go - 测试 NewForConfigAndClient 使用自定义 httpClient\\n- [ ] T004: 实现 clientset_test.go - 测试 NewForConfigOrDie 正常情况\\n- [ ] T005: 实现 clientset_test.go - 测试 NewForConfigOrDie 无效配置时 panic\\n- [ ] T006: 实现 clientset_test.go - 测试 New 使用 rest.Interface\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Phase 2: AgentRuntime CRUD 测试\\n\\n- [ ] T007: 创建 agentruntime_test.go - 测试 Create AgentRuntime 资源\\n- [ ] T008: 创建 agentruntime_test.go - 测试 Get AgentRuntime 资源\\n- [ ] T009: 创建 agentruntime_test.go - 测试