**Group accessor:** `RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\\n37: \\n38: ---\\n39: \\n40: ## Typed client — `runtime/v1alpha1`\\n41: \\n42: ### `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` (`clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alph...\n  Line 7: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775884559618,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2850888eeffe6nUnso1RhMHTNb\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7af7a022001EnhMqdmzzVCNjk\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7af78bca001ICMmzj1WlWakVK\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2850888eeffe6nUnso1RhMHTNb\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_a937a06b724c469694fdb226\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Proposal: E2E Integration Testing Framework\\n\\n## AR Information\\n- **AR ID**: AR-041\\n- **Module**: test/e2e\\n- **Language**: Go\\n- **Size**: L\\n\\n## 1. Purpose\\n\\nThis proposal outlines the development of an End-to-End (E2E) integration testing framework for the agentcube project. The E2E tests will validate the complete workflow of the Kubernetes custom resources `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter` from the perspective of a real user or external system interacting with the cluster.\\n\\n### Goals\\n- Verify the complete lifecycle of `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter` resources\\n- Ensure the client-go generated code works correctly in real cluster scenarios\\n- Validate controller behavior through API interactions\\n- Provide regression testing for system integrations\\n\\n## 2. Scope\\n\\n### In Scope\\n1. **Test Resources**\\n   - `AgentRuntime` CRUD operations (Create, Read, Update, Delete)\\n   - `CodeInterpreter` CRUD operations\\n   - Status updates and condition propagation\\n   - Resource watching and event handling\\n\\n2. **Test Infrastructure**\\n   - Test framework setup using Go's testing package\\n   - Kubernetes test environment (kind cluster or similar)\\n   - Test fixtures and helpers for resource creation\\n   - Cleanup and teardown utilities\\n\\n3. **Test Scenarios**\\n   - Basic CRUD operations via cl