y` → `/opsx:verify` → `/opsx:archive`），\\n **量化 8 个阶段（ST-0~ST-7）× 5 个维度的 Token 消耗**，为 Token 提效研究提供评估基线。\\n \\n-## 核心演进：v3.0 Reinforced Evaluation\\n+## v5.1 架构\\n \\n-v3.0 引入了 **Realism Guard (现实主义护栏)** 架构，确保评测数据的真实性与代码的实质性完成度：\\n+```\\n+engine.py (benchmark driver)\\n+  → adapters/*.py (CLI tool subprocess)\\n+    → LiteLLM Proxy JSONL (authoritative token log, port 4000)\\n+      → auditor.py (time-window filtering, cost calculation)\\n+        → _full.json (schema-compliant output)\\n+```\\n \\n-1.  **Session Isolation (会话隔离)**: 每个评测轮次强制清理环境，避免历史缓存干扰 Token 统计。\\n-2.  **LOC Delta Gate (代码增量门禁)**: 实时监控每个阶段的代码产出，禁止 AI 通过“伪造存根 (Stubs)”或“空实现”来刷低 Token 消耗。\\n-3.  **Penalty Retry (惩罚性重试)**: 一旦检测到低 LOC 或空代码产出，自动触发“惩罚性 Prompt”，强制模型重新进行实质性开发。\\n-4.  **Cumulative Turn Summation (转录累加)**: 精确统计 Agentic Loop 中每一轮对话的累加消耗，而非仅取最后一轮。\\n+**核心特性**:\\n+- **LiteLLM Proxy 为唯一权威数据源**: 每次 API 调用均记录精确 token 用量\\n+- **Native CLI 兜底解析**: 适配器从 CLI 工具输出中解析 token，作为 Proxy 不可用时的回退\\n+- **Re...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/reports/sdd_tee_report.json:\n  Line 458:       \"id\": \"AR-041\",\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/scripts/report.py:\n  Line 136:     {\"id\": \"AR-041\", \"name\": \"E2E 集成测试\", \"module\": \"test/e2e\", \"lang\": \"Go\",\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/claude-code_claude-sonnet-4_20260410T040627Z_full.json:\n  Line 458:       \"id\": \"AR-041\",\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/claude-code_claude-sonnet-4_20260410T040623Z_full.json:\n  Line 458:       \"id\": \"AR-041\",\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/claude-code_claude-sonnet-4_20260410T040502Z_full.json:\n  Line 458:       \"id\": \"AR-041\",\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/claude-code_claude-sonnet-4_20260410T040431Z_full.json:\n  Line 458:       \"id\": \"AR-041\",\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v4.0/gemini-cli_gemini-3.1-pro_20260327T100000Z_full.json:\n  Line 6594:       \"ar_id\": \"AR-041\",\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v4.0/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_2026032